---
title: Jerk Chicken Legs with Tropical Rice, Pineapple Salsa & Roasted Green Beans
description: This week, we’re taking you on a trip to the Caribbean...from the comfort of your own kitchen! Jerk-spiced chicken legs are roasted to juicy, crispy perfection, then topped with a spicy-sweet pineapple salsa. On the side, there’s tender roasted green beans and aromatic coconut rice spiked with pineapple and lime juice. Together, it’s a full-blown flavor explosion. One bite will transport your taste buds to warm weather, white sand, and turquoise water—no passport required.
